snippet.title: Amber Heard Drags DISNEY Into Johnny Depp Defamation Case?!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard's legal team has subpoenaed Disney. She wants all communication between The Mouse House and Johnny Depp during Pirates of the Caribbean 4 filming so they can go digging for evidence against him. Has she just gotten herself black listed from future Disney projects? Probably. Mickey doesn't like to be threatened...
